330
00:26:46,636 --> 00:26:48,302
Tom:
Where they all go?

331
00:26:48,304 --> 00:26:51,238
Clay: Maybe we got lucky and they all dropped off,

332
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:54,774
you know,
when they lost the signal like at the train station.

333
00:27:11,225 --> 00:27:14,158
Tom. Tom.

