00:34:38,762 --> 00:34:41,062
exactly where
we were that fast.

386
00:34:41,064 --> 00:34:44,231
<i>I mean, it's not like they</i>
<i>were watching us or anything.</i>

387
00:34:44,233 --> 00:34:46,299
Not with their own
eyes anyway.

388
00:34:46,301 --> 00:34:48,401
Not with their own--

389
